casebody.data:
Laurenceville Cement Co., Respondent, v. Parker, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 12, 1890.) Appeal from city court, general term.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

B. Doran Killian, for appellant. Arnoux, Ritch & Woodford, for respondent.

■ No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs. Affirming 10 N. Y. Supp. 831.
